<div id='description' ><h2>Sony FIT Multi-Flip Ultrabook/Tablet 15.5" FHD i5-4200U Features</h2><div class='trunc_wrap'><span itemprop="description"><b>No compromise</b> : First and foremost, it's a productive and entertaining VAIO that's packed with uncompromising features. Speed through daily documents and photo editing using latest generation Intel® Core™ i processors.<br />
<b>Flip to convert</b> : When you want to browse the web or explore apps by touch, switch to tablet mode. The screen flips out in one seamless and fluid movement.<br />
<b>Type around the clock</b> : Type, blog, surf the web, anytime of day or night. All so easy on an isolation keyboard with precise key spacing and backlighting.<br />
<br />


